- Most of the time static pod has name suffix with node name
- Kubelet config file is located: /var/lib/kubelet/config.yaml
- To specifcy command use: kubectl run ... --command sleep 1000
- Static pod are managed directly by the kubelet daemon on a specific npde, without api server obersving them
- Oberserving staticpod behavior docker ps
- kubectl run --generator=run-pod/v1 www-1 --image=nginx:1.16 creating pod for kubectl version 1.18
